01:35:27.889 --> 01:35:30.391
Pumpkin.

01:35:33.311 --> 01:35:35.229
Jackson.

01:35:59.712 --> 01:36:02.673
Does this tie go?

01:36:05.510 --> 01:36:06.844
Yeah.

01:36:09.097 --> 01:36:11.515
You look real nice.

01:36:11.599 --> 01:36:15.436
I'll come with you to the funeral
